elements.name: disclaimer
elements.title:
IMPORTANT: Have you used GitHub Copilot for your personal or previous professional projects before this evaluation at UBP?

IMPORTANT: If "No," please do not proceed with the following questions and submit the survey. Your insights will be valuable in future surveys as you gain experience with GitHub Copilot throughout this evaluation period.
